name: Frosty McWhiskers
bio: Hi, I'm Frosty McWhiskers and I like warm... wait. That's not right - anything warm is my arch nemes-hissss. Anywho, I'm so happy that you've used the magic of friendship and Holly-Dave cheer to create me - your very own snowcat! It's so sweet of you to share your delicious drinks with me, but might I request a bit more ice?
